T16TD4386E:317a-1: tsandra go mi pra ni dh'a na n'a ma /
T16TD4386E:317a-3: btsun pa zla ba'i smon lam zhes bya ba /
T16TD4386E:317a-4: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T16TD4386E:317a-5: srid pa'i las ni nyam nga yis //
T16TD4386E:317a-6: gang dang gang du nyer skye ba //
T16TD4386E:317a-7: de dang der ni skyes pa dang //
T16TD4386E:317a-8: dad dang dbang po tshang ba dang //
T16TD4386E:317a-9: bzo dang sgyu rtsal kun mngon shes //
T16TD4386E:317a-10: bstan bcos kun la 'jigs med dang //
T16TD4386E:317a-11: 'dod pa kun la rgyab phyogs shing //
T16TD4386E:317a-12: dngos kun yongs su gtong ba dang //
T16TD4386E:317a-13: dran dang ldan zhing bden smra dang /
T16TD4386E:317a-14: sems can rnams kyis mthong na dga' //
T16TD4386E:317a-15: byang chub sems kyis rnam brgyan pa'i //
T16TD4386E:317a-16: dge ba'i bshes gnyen bsten pa dang //
T16TD4386E:317a-17: dul ba'i spyod dang yang dag ldan //
T16TD4386E:317a-18: blo bzang skye ba gtsang ma dran //
T16TD4386E:317a-19: sdig pa'i las la 'jigs byed pas //
T16TD4386E:317a-20: spyod pa dge ba'i spyod yul can //
T16TD4386E:317a-21: mthar yang bla med rtogs pa yis //
T16TD4386E:317a-22: pha rol phyin pa bcu bsten pas //
T16TD4386E:317a-23: 'gro la gcig tu bde ba yi //
T16TD4386E:317a-24: g-yo med mgon po thob par gyur //
T16TD4386E:317a-25: bdag ni bran dang mor ma gyur //
T16TD4386E:317a-26: blun dang yul ngan skye ba dang //
T16TD4386E:317a-27: sangs rgyas 'byung la lkog ma gyur //
T16TD4386E:317a-28: nam du'ang lta ba log ma gyur //
T16TD4386E:317a-29: 'dod med tshul ldan sangs rgyas rgyur //
T16TD4386E:317a-30: pha rol 'dod pa'i rdzas longs spyod //
T16TD4386E:317a-31: sems can nyam thag byed 'gyur ba'i //
T16TD4386E:317a-32: 'dod pa'i slong mo bdag mi spyod //
T16TD4386E:317a-33: sems can rnams la byams goms shing //
T16TD4386E:317a-34: rgyu med rang bzhin sangs rgyas dang //
T16TD4386E:317b-1: rigs chen blo nor skye ba dang //
T16TD4386E:317b-2: skye ba skye bar lus mdzes shing //
T16TD4386E:317b-3: bde gshegs mang po'i snyan ngag byed //
T16TD4386E:317b-4: skye zhing skye ba dang ldan par //
T16TD4386E:317b-5: gang du sangs rgyas lhar byed pa'i //
T16TD4386E:317b-6: rigs der bdag ni skye ba dang //
T16TD4386E:317b-7: skye ba dang ni skye ba ru //
T16TD4386E:317b-8: chos lnga po ni mi spong zhing //
T16TD4386E:317b-9: bsod nams ye shes stobs dang ni //
T16TD4386E:317b-10: brtson 'grus byang chub sems lnga po //
T16TD4386E:317b-11: ji ltar thams cad mkhyen pa yi //
T16TD4386E:317b-12: zhabs thob pa yi thabs de bzhin //
T16TD4386E:317b-13: de ltar bdag gis thabs kyis ni //
T16TD4386E:317b-14: thub pa'i dbang po'i zhabs thob shog / btsun pa zla ba'i smon lam zhes bya ba rdzogs so /
T16TD4386E:317b-16: // / rab tu bsngags pa'i gnas chen po nye ba'i 'thung gcod dpal bal po yam bu'i grong khyer du /
T16TD4386E:317b-17: bal po'i pandi ta dzee ka karna'i zhal snga nas dang /
T16TD4386E:317b-18: bod kyi lo ts'a ba sh'akya'i dge slong nyi ma rgyal mtshan dpal bzang pos bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o//
